ActEmployment Insurance Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Employment Insurance (Fishing) Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE (FISHING) REGULATIONS in order to (1) support full implementation of the amendments to the Employment Insurance parental benefits; and (2) ensure that fishers who claim Employment Insurance benefits are treated as other claimants.
